163
00:21:38,744 --> 00:21:40,165
[SPEAKER_03]: I wanted that job badly.

164
00:21:41,086 --> 00:21:49,413
[SPEAKER_03]: So I was called into the interview room, and I was told to have a seat, and we had a conversation.

165
00:21:49,974 --> 00:21:55,399
