166
00:21:55,699 --> 00:21:56,980
[SPEAKER_03]: We were stewardesses at the time.

167
00:21:57,340 --> 00:21:59,122
[SPEAKER_03]: Why do you want to be a stewardess?

168
00:21:59,622 --> 00:22:03,306
[SPEAKER_03]: And of course, the answer was, I love people.

169
00:22:07,845 --> 00:22:09,466
[SPEAKER_03]: So I love people.

170
00:22:09,566 --> 00:22:15,949
